{"tid":1619933,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"禁蒙面法唔係冇位比我地打文宣！！！","createTime":"2019-10-04T08:59:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T10:29:40.000Z","uid":1411,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e78a9a7354309f34eb1cdc320b1d96cf0c0c3118","tid":1619933,"uid":1411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T08:59:55.000Z","msg":"禁蒙面法唔係冇位比我地打文宣！！！<br />\n我知緊急法個重要性係大多好<br />\n但係禁蒙面法我地都可以大文ｐｉｓｈ文宣<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n警方由６月９吮開始已經夙左唔撚知幾多ｔｇ<br />\n又有唔知幾多ｔｇ比人發現過期<br />\n仲要依家美國已經誚明唔會賣比香港<br />\n之後入貨已經唔會知係邊度黎既貨<br />\n<br />\n每次戰線<br />\n唔計埋班和理非<br />\n起碼８成都係用緊豬咀保護緊自己<br />\n<br />\n我地係要打政府禁止市民保護自己<br />\n而強迫市民吸入各種致命性有毒化學氣體！！<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">政府</span>已經決定要毒害並殺死香港市民</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">強調今次唔係警方！！係林鄭！！！</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"a724ce1794940f9a08adbaaf851db0387b4de9e0","tid":1619933,"uid":245033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:01:27.000Z","msg":"如果我冇耳殘<br />\n我係聽到<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">而家香港唔係緊急狀態</span></span><br />\n肯定仲有得打"},{"pid":"38d1f69b34183b43886f984eb6bc8fcdaeaf365c","tid":1619933,"uid":293698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:02:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"abb335d1aab46cfa627524e9259c92e21cfe86b8","tid":1619933,"uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:02:05.000Z","msg":"除此之外，《禁蒙面法》料惹來極大爭議，可即時把社會討論焦點，由目前最熱門的警員開實彈槍擊傷中五學生，轉移至立法行動，變相把「擋子彈」的角色由警隊交波至政府官員，即使未必能完全解決問題，至少可讓捱轟多時的警隊喘一口氣。<br />\n<br />\n今日信報<br />\n<br />\n請唔好忘記哩一單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78a5228a232f4e1265e8e4a18796c2f1162e5d9a","tid":1619933,"uid":1411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:02:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"187a99b5b970efec7529da5620ca2bd45cd7b079","tid":1619933,"uid":1411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:03:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0f5c87fddae575e8b980dff5c53f1f42e1bc4f0","tid":1619933,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:03:21.000Z","msg":"除此之外，《禁蒙面法》料惹來極大爭議，可即時把社會討論焦點，由目前最熱門的警員開實彈槍擊傷中五學生，轉移至立法行動，變相把「擋子彈」的角色由警隊交波至政府官員，即使未必能完全解決問題，至少可讓捱轟多時的警隊喘一口氣。<br />\n<br />\n今日信報<br />\n<br />\n請唔好忘記哩一單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30ed8523d56f8a73f207ca93bc4bb6d8474136da","tid":1619933,"uid":186088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T10:29:40.000Z","msg":"pushhhh"}]}